---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { t } from '../../i18n/utils';

const lang = 'en';
---

<PageLayout title={t(lang, 'nav.about')}>
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display mb-8 text-center">
      {t(lang, 'about.title')}
    </h1>

    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Replace with your real story -->
    <div class="space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg">
        {t(lang, 'about.intro')}
      </p>

      <div class="border-l-2 border-accent-gold pl-6 my-8">
        <p class="text-text-primary italic">
          <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Your personal quote or philosophy -->
          "Building in public. One confused commit at a time."
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text-primary mt-12 mb-4">
        The Journey
      </h2>
      <p>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Your story -->
        This is where you tell your story. How did you get here? What drives you to make murder mystery games? What's your background?
      </p>
      <p>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: More story -->
        Talk about your learning journey with AI. How you're building everything yourself. The failures, the wins, the 3am commits.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text-primary mt-12 mb-4">
        Why Murder Mysteries?
      </h2>
      <p>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Your why -->
        Why this genre? What do you love about it? What do you want players to feel?
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text-primary mt-12 mb-4">
        The Tools
      </h2>
      <p>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Your process -->
        Everything on this site — design, code, games, writing — is made by me with AI as my collaborator. I'm learning as I go.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
        <li>Site: Astro + Tailwind</li>
        <li>Design: Penpot</li>
        <li>AI: Claude, Midjourney, ElevenLabs</li>
        <li>Games: Typst, lots of research, too much coffee</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display text-text-primary mt-12 mb-4">
        Connect
      </h2>
      <p>
        <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Links -->
        Follow the chaos on <a href="https://dominatedbycline.github.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-gold hover:text-accent-gold-hover">my blog</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
